eview is conducted upon SOC/ROC \n\nand based on the assessing clinician\u2019s professional judgment, potential or actual clinically significant \nmedication issues are identified. \no  Examples may include, but are not limited to: \n\n\u00ad  Patient\u2019s list of medications from the inpatient facility discharge instructions DO NOT match the \n\nmedications the patient shows the clinician at the SOC/ROC assessment visit.", "type": "Document"}}